{"tid":1390613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人申請移民台灣急增　比去年平均增近三成","createTime":"2019-07-31T07:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T07:46:32.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"babe673a0b3d04cee86dde5b9735957504ad45e1","tid":1390613,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190731/s00004/c55b04d9a1181a3c8e189d7f3471b0a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190731%2Fs00004%2Fc55b04d9a1181a3c8e189d7f3471b0a2.jpg&h=d4f3379a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特區政府修訂《逃犯條例》引發移民潮，據台灣內政部移民署資料，截至今日（31日）上午為止，今年申請數量平均增加29.8%，7月更比6月多出114人，增加42.3%。<br />\n<br />\n台媒報道，據移民署資料，本年度香港居民申請居留台灣的個案不斷上升，每個月都超出去年數量。今年4月有286宗申請、5月有260宗、6月有269宗、7月更達383宗，申請數量幾乎都超過去年同期五成；7月比6月多出114人，增加42.3%。<br />\n<br />\n內政部長徐國勇表示，今年申請數量平均增加29.8%，移民署居留許可率亦較去年增加57%。他續說，因台灣的自由民主為香港人所羨慕期待，亦抱有很高的評價，加上台灣與香港居住環境比較相近，無論飲食、交通、氣候等亦熟悉，因此將台灣當作重要選擇，推測是今年申請居留數量不斷增加的原因。"},{"pid":"530a390285fb4f0665d97b2b30055139adacc779","tid":1390613,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:41:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190731/s00004/1564558253046/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190731%2Fs00004%2F1564558253046%2F&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qndjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=f93b0e20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190731%2Fs00004%2F1564558253046%2F&h=b65e4ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190731/s00004/1564558253046/</a>"},{"pid":"ac5b5a1e230f0d4e58285f3c81b5b5a6e67fdcec","tid":1390613,"uid":8745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:42:54.000Z","msg":"雖然一國兩制冇台灣人信，中共仲可以武力攻台，到時走去邊？"},{"pid":"519426f3431ea4f59bd61d402d5852cf8d46e206","tid":1390613,"uid":113626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"香港人走去台灣好易, 當地物價又唔高<br />\n你係香港有幾百萬可能係果到已經夠過一世<br />\n移民個難處永遠都係搵工困難, 當地人肯唔肯比機會你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4943970d5acf63dbfbf91cfd7e36c1d6e1dcb9e","tid":1390613,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"用台灣黎做中轉站，冇話唔可以再移"},{"pid":"a33db70f67288138f5aa3ffda6eb540b5e9f85ed","tid":1390613,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:46:32.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qndjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=234e451a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。"}]}